goal.tools.unittest.result

Class AgentTestResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.tools.unittest.result.AgentTestResult

  • public class AgentTestResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores the result of a AgentTest. A test produces a list of a AssertTestResult and an exception if the agent under test ran into an exception. The test is considered passed if all AssertTestResult are passed and no exception was thrown.
    Author:
    M.P. Korstanje
